00:19.840 --> 00:21.960
Our volunteer army risked life and death for Your Majesty

00:22.360 --> 00:24.360
Only a few old brothers survived

00:24.680 --> 00:25.360
I don't believe

00:25.480 --> 00:26.840
Your Majesty would abandon us

00:26.960 --> 00:27.360
Right

00:27.640 --> 00:28.160
Let's go

