Kneel down

00:45.480 --> 00:47.760
The sages' books are for reading

00:47.960 --> 00:50.400
Not for you to actually use

00:52.600 --> 00:55.280
His Majesty sent you to reform in the Chen family's stronghold

00:56.440 --> 00:59.640
